entry.title: Philippines allows limited religious gatherings in GCQ areas as 'ber' months begin

media:group.media:title: Philippines allows limited religious gatherings in GCQ areas as 'ber' months begin
media:group.media:description:

Roque also enumerated during the Palace briefing some of the establishments that may operate in select areas starting September 1.
